{"tid":1656652,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線—Facebook","createTime":"2019-10-15T16:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T11:18:03.000Z","uid":307203,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"9251acb04a23be555ed0e20065606e8f3d285f29","tid":1656652,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:48:16.000Z","msg":"巴打唔好意思 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望你唔好介意我抄你嘅post<br />\n<br />\n原post:【簡易文宣】本土戰線&mdash;FaceBook!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648722</a><br />\n<br />\n前言.<br />\n小弟覺得原post 只係集中於我哋嗰邊，但Facebook作為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">世界主流社交網站</span></span>，其實我哋同樣可以有Twitter同Reddit 一樣文宣效果，所以都要打埋呢一次戰線<br />\n<br />\n但如果大家想加入其他國際文宣戰線，以下為加入方式<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">Twitter</span></span> 共識channel <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLCcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=52d149a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n<br />\n【突發】每晚十點 全民Twitter ！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656182</a><br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Reddit</span></span> 文宣部 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/redditmansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fredditmansyunzou&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLCcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=009ecf7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/redditmansyunzou</a><br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線要人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656389</a><br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">英文文宣Channel</span></span>：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo_int&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLCcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=4b11931f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論本土或國際戰線都係一個非常簡單嘅文宣方式，同埋你就算<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幾懶都好，你都一定有一個Facebook account</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n如果你怕被人用Facebook post 篤灰，你都可以開多一個account<br />\n<br />\n正文.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">本士:</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">A.黃絲</span></span><br />\nFacebook其實喺和理非聚集地，係一個可以好好做文宣嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，想邀請大家一齊做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好簡單 但喺成效大</span></span><br />\n<br />\n步驟/注意事項：<br />\n<br />\n1/ <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">搵啲出名嘅page</span></span><br />\n例如 立場 蘋果 獨媒 金水 大J 民安 天佑 等等<br />\n<br />\n或者中立同扮黄page <br />\n例如 明報 信報 01 經濟 Now 有線<br />\n<br />\n總之要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全方位無死角</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2/ <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搵個新嘅post</span></span><br />\n例如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0d6MOQc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0d6MOQc.png&h=ff8b21f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n越新嘅post效果越好<br />\n<br />\n3/ <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">留言擺文宣圖 然後自己like自己</span></span><br />\n例如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k45qjXC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk45qjXC.png&h=377df145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4/ <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">見到同路人擺文宣 記得要like返</span></span><br />\n好重要 因為得你一個自己like自己<br />\n曝光率好低<br />\n所以見到手足擺文宣圖記得要like<br />\n<br />\n5/ 遇到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武手足裝修</span></strong></span>的影片時<br />\n留言 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警自導自演 一定喺臥底！ 黑警辛苦曬啦</span></strong></span> 等等<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為fb嘅和理非好相信大部分勇武行動都喺狗做嘅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要依個風向延續不斷 再加插啲解釋點解要裝修嘅文宣<br />\n例如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3UEOhMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3UEOhMA.jpg&h=73061ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地唔會點失民意</span><br />\n<br />\n效果：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.和理非遊行同行動人數大增</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2.互相團結不分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">B.藍絲</span></strong></span><br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">打破同温層</span></span><br />\n<br />\n拯救藍絲！正式進入：「Facebook連儂牆計劃」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1580225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1580225</a><br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">Report</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n得閒就去report人哋， 總之搞到佢哋似點新聞咁樣死不翻生<br />\n例如以下立場報過嘅page<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E8%87%89%E6%9B%B8%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88-fb-page-group/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E8%2587%2589%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%2590%2588-fb-page-group%2F&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLCcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=c1efe035\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E8%2587%2589%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%2590%2588-fb-page-group%2F&h=ef5b3414\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E8%87%89%E6%9B%B8%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88-fb-page-group/</a><br />\n<br />\n不過仲有好多嘅，總之大家見到就即刻report<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仇恨言論</span></span><br />\n同埋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfUbGmP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfUbGmP.png&h=909e76ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">分化對家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然人哋都不斷分化我哋， 點解我哋唔去分化人哋呢？<br />\n<br />\n我哋可以順便<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開多個account去扮藍絲</span></strong></span>，分化對家同帶風向，搞到佢哋都要捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n可以參考以下post：<br />\n1.[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n<br />\n2.[文宣] 手足們係時候分化班狗同冇腦藍絲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1237194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1237194</a><br />\n<br />\n3. [香城OL新職業]【符號爭奪戰】誠招幻象師! 黃絲係我地; 藍絲? 都係我地!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335220</a><br />\n<br />\n4.［文宣升級］長輩式反攻保皇FB Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223616</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記得要用埋我哋嘅長輩圖去分化同反攻啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">B.國際</span></span>:<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">上去國際傳媒、NGO同埋世界政客嘅page</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如 BBC CNN ABC Foxnews 紐約時報 泰晤士報 國際特赦組織 Ted Cruz 蔡英文 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">搵個新嘅有關香港嘅post</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Like 同埋打留言或放文宣或者Meme圖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方向：<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港係自由世界嘅前線</span></span>， <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係東方西柏林</span></span><br />\n例如：<br />\n美國國會議員將香港類比為冷戰高峰時期嘅西柏林！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1653833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1653833</a><br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人道危機</span></span><br />\n例如：<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n【國際線行動】應盡快整理612後警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒到埋身</span></span><br />\n總之要令到全世界都知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共會搞到佢哋利益受損同埋失去自由</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要製造出如同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當年西方對蘇聯嘅恐懼</span></span><br />\n例如：<br />\n［國際文宣］用英文整合中共係國際各個層面唧控制 令外國人都會有身受其害嘅覺悟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1492342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1492342</a><br />\n<br />\n最好要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">專注五毛出征嗰啲新聞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如NBA ( 通常都係雞毛蒜皮嘅小事)<br />\n<br />\n因為官方引導佢哋搞完嘢後，仲要叫官媒同埋外交部出嚟大聲譴責同恐嚇，通常都會搞出一個小型風波<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋嘅責任就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將場火越燒越大</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n總結.<br />\n所以如果大家懶嘅話或者唔想開其他平台嘅account嘅話，請大家盡做Facebook 文宣"},{"pid":"126aa85491b7ca7dd3a1e029573878f25248abdc","tid":1656652,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54888b4c4b81136a0081570b354695bcc961ae1d","tid":1656652,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1cc2d83017e9e426af37cdc2b7b5e4e33fe06b9e","tid":1656652,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:48:43.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5d19f48525efdc46cb2ed66ed4c31f8e7f190a","tid":1656652,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6376e156b6f097f20474edb2355def8063a8ebac","tid":1656652,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa258fe064560c279bb8784c258f8e6e20cc559","tid":1656652,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6083b331d54fbe2de125c70101d12f44d19cb525","tid":1656652,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jDFeEBr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjDFeEBr.jpg&h=ee3f43b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10a6da276149ac92c93568d7f40d74a431a9dfac","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\nFACEBOOK戰線要人"},{"pid":"71a06fbfc658c3cf1eac021c2b12ad9b66e5332e","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:31:24.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"607c472aad3cdbf95d92e43ca4fcdd332eba321f","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:31:40.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d4cb25986d3dd4d6cbcfff21049d50b840320124","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:31:50.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d192a0cd4e486ad2c740094decff50844ad3be06","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"ddf8512405f1829a3732d591501be56097a278aa","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:32:11.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"a279dcc6fa1a74fb67d5822f6571b885f5f1bad5","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:32:45.000Z","msg":"《人手轉載》<br />\n<br />\n希望大家維持嗌五大訴求：<br />\n1.缺一不可本來就有環環相扣既意思，正如林鄭撤回咗條例，都唔會改嗌四大訴求，簡單啲講，呢句野既結果一係5，一係0，冇其他。<br />\n2.解散警隊呢個訴求並唔夠實際同具體，基本上五大訴求達成就已經可以蓋括埋解散警隊既效果，正如一開始第五個訴求係林鄭下台，大家都覺得呢個訴求唔實際，所以改做雙普選，所以，我地係唔需要特登加多一個訴求落去，咁先比到人睇我地一直爭取緊既係具體、可行、實際既訴求。<br />\n解散警隊可以獨立嗌，代表我地對警隊嚴重不滿，但唔好將佢當做第六大訴求。<br />\n3.國際啱啱先開始知到我地爭取緊既係五大訴求而唔係林鄭一句撤回就咁簡單，所以維持五大訴求先比到人一種由始此終都係爭取緊同一樣野既觀感。"},{"pid":"a83c215e81144093e9c70f10563bc934dc060d9b","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:32:55.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"0968c00608b520eb235e508163bebde86824fa06","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:33:06.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"fb55cd352773eb43e3bbb4762b8a45daf7a6756d","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"3b920ee7ce0d6631284752e2eca1726875546915","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:33:26.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"fcbff9a5b72f23baf83d3bb69208e7e40062f2d6","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:33:58.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"055ffc7c00a517ffc3b81fdfaae1c62c5fd88806","tid":1656652,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316dd202001d2bb6d1ed773547d6214cfe9c37ed","tid":1656652,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10a6da276149ac92c93568d7f40d74a431a9dfac","tid":1656652,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\nFACEBOOK戰線要人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打"},{"pid":"c9ae55468bff4553306ef4406fbe337bb4021b34","tid":1656652,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f